parameters.name: Translation
parameters.description: Base freq. of freq. bandwidth (0.0, 125.454, 250.908, and 501.816 kHz)

parameters.name: Resolution
parameters.description: Number of bits used when digitizing waveform (8-bit, 4-bit, or 1-bit)

parameters.name: Ant_B_Field_Angle
parameters.description: Total angle between antenna used for WBD measurement and measured B field direction

parameters.name: Ant_Xgse_Angle
parameters.description: Total angle between the Xgse axis and the antenna direction

parameters.name: Ant_YZgse_Plane_Angle
parameters.description: Total angle between Ygse axis and the projection of the antenna direction in the Ygse-Zgse plane

parameters.name: DC_Offset
parameters.description: DC Offset used when converting from raw digital values to calibrated data

parameters.name: DATA_QUALITY
parameters.description: Data Quality: 0 = OK, 1 = clipped or questionable, 2 = bad data point.
